@71   = ~Slow and Steady~
@72   = ~This heavy-headed hammer looks like it was used for construction on the Palisade, and it's possible that none of the workers were aware of its enchanted nature.  While this weapon is a little slower and heavier than a warhammer, its swing is true and does more damage when it hits.  A single tap from this hammer creates a clear, ringing note. 

