@75   = ~Caballus' Whispering Staff~
@76   = ~This ironwood staff was once held by the goblin sorcerer Caballus, and it still bears the stink of his touch.  Trails of runes encircle the staff like snakes, and aside from a single minor rune of accuracy and another of wounding, the rest appear to be nonsense syllables and bunk.  The staff is surprisingly light and well-balanced for its size, and it can be held easily in one hand. 

