@79   = ~Cornugon Hide Armor~
@80   = ~There is great mystery surrounding this leather armor. No one knows how or where it came into existence.  What is known is that the leather was cut from the hide of a Cornugon. The armor is colored a deep black and riddled with very tough, barbed scales.  In addition, it has an unusual, very light, vinegary smell.

Those that have worn the Cornugon Hide were bestowed with a rather high invulnerability to non-magical weapons and the ability to slowly regenerate from injuries. 

